    <briefdescription>
<para>Parameters for synchronizing with specific periodic advertising subevents. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This struct contains the parameters used to synchronize with a subset of subevents in periodic advertising. It includes the periodic advertising properties, the number of subevents to sync to, and the list of subevents that the controller should synchronize with.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>Used in <ref refid="group__bt__gap_1ga731f4b37a9e5cc13a6816ea23f751b0b" kindref="member">bt_le_per_adv_sync_subevent</ref> function to control synchronization. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
